{"tid":559981,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【 戀 外 籍 男 】裕 美 不 會 衝 動 閃 婚","createTime":"2018-02-13T16:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T07:42:24.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"32af77e0f63ee6e84c13bd0adaa2f8be6fcc6ae8","tid":559981,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"裕美最近與外籍男友Alex蜜運中，今日春風滿面出席華星冰室分店開幕活動。裕美笑言Alex已被偷拍過幾次，大家認識了大半年時間，最初無想過發展感情，「不過現在也幾好，他是香港工作的，所以不是遠距離戀愛，和他一齊學識好多英文和意大利文。（是否浪漫之人？）不是，他份人好慢熱，（慢熱便不會閃婚？）不會，大家都知我又不是未試過，不會為結婚而結婚，以前想法太童真，現在會想得實際一點。」<br />\n<br />\n提到兩人早前結伴旅行，裕美稱半工作半旅遊，主要拍片介紹當地。問到是否Alex操刀？裕美說：「是我自己拍，他經常拍到我腳又短又粗，不過現在進步不少。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180212/s00009/52fcf028ddcfaab0e2be48d03252e5c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180212%2Fs00009%2F52fcf028ddcfaab0e2be48d03252e5c1.jpg&h=6af45202&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca92c4df5e369a7bf9eec88b3e0ba1935554823b","tid":559981,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"晚晚含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defa71572e25796d73c2ac85302a6b8c1ddad0f0","tid":559981,"uid":122445,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"點解佢依家係咁既樣 <br />\n好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"be55db4f4327c3c2d9411987c46e9d1eda2f4acd","tid":559981,"uid":121473,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:32:40.000Z","msg":"呢個係裕美？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中好似唔係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a719a0241105b6eec4053b7dbf4cffc1fd43eb","tid":559981,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T17:15:31.000Z","msg":"整過容"},{"pid":"735bb97aa039c0f9956daed0b0555f11a134d4b1","tid":559981,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike